Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.65,0:00:47.06,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Chiya-chan's going to...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.52,0:00:49.02,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,be a magical girl!?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.03,0:00:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Miracle Chronicle!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.95,0:00:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovelin, Goblin.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.49,0:00:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Debauchery abound!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.79,0:01:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Girl Chiya appears!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.13,0:01:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Underestimate me,\N and you'll go up in flames.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.46,0:01:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.17,0:01:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.30,0:01:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,With all of us...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.89,0:01:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,working together...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.35,0:01:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.69,0:01:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.36,0:01:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll make this world into a Chiya-ry fairy tale! {Get it? Chiya-ry = cheery}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.91,0:01:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.75,0:01:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiya-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.08,0:01:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mafuyu-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.84,0:01:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not happening.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.63,0:01:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what you were going on about.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.09,0:02:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In the first place, Mafuyu's retirement and \Nmy next assignment are two separate issues.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.06,0:02:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Besides, Mafuyu isn't going \Nto retire anytime soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We should just have fun for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.85,0:02:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have as much fun as possible
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.57,0:02:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,messing with both \NYuzuka-chan and Chiya-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.78,0:02:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have fun... \Nmessing with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.32,0:02:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning on doing \Nafter you graduate from high school?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about helping with the shop.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I can just take over at some point.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Take over?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.96,0:02:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I can spend all day playing games.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Viva my second life.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.63,0:02:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard him.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.09,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,He really is a waste of air.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We had the shop all to ourselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,For a weird reason, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiya-chan, are you running errands?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.39,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.48,0:02:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My father is coming home from being at sea for the first time in a year.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So my mom said she'd make us a feast.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yay...?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I must be on my way.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.49,0:03:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, one thing did happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Something good, I mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.21,0:03:14.63,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,900)}Has anything good happened to you \Nsince you became a magical girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if has much to do with being \Na magical girl, but since Miton came...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My father comes home late,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.26,0:03:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and I used to eat dinner alone,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.76,0:03:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's kind of nice that Miton \Nenjoys eating my cooking so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuka...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because your cooking
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.57,0:03:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is so much better than the \Nliteral garbage I was eating.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He had that coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.58,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it! Nothing good has come of this at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To be continued!
